Quickstrike:




Quickstrike transformed to robot mode, and handed the three disks to 
Megatron. "Then ah'll call th' others fer more help." he said. He opened his 
comm-link to the Predacon's on Megatron's group. "Shredder, Lightmare, 
Mantella, Stingtra, Drazom, Sinester, Sinesis, get t' out location. We's 
need yer help. Watch yer backs so Hell Beast don't follow ya."
